courses.learning_outcomes:
By the end of this course, students will be able to:

1. understand the content and the rationale behind the Hong Kong secondary school mathematics curriculum;
2. construct lesson plans by selecting and sequencing "big ideas" to teach in school mathematics;
3. determine prerequisite knowledge and skills for learning different mathematics topics;
4. use effective teaching methods and instructional aids such as experiments and models to teach mathematics concepts;
5. identify the common difficulties in mathematics learning among secondary school students;
6. construct tests and other diagnosis to evaluate the effectiveness of mathematics learning and teaching

學生修畢本科後，能夠：
1. 了解香港中學數學課程背後之理念及其所涵蓋內容

2. 學會透過撰擇及鋪排一些重要數學思想來設計教案

3. 掌握不同數學課題所需的基本知識及技能

4. 運用不同的有效教學法如實驗及模型去教授數學概念

5. 明晰中學生常見的數學學習困難

6. 透過測試及分析去評估數學教與學之效能

By the end of this course, students will be able to:
1. use information and communication technology to teach mathematics effectively;
2. design mathematical rich pedagogical tasks by using mathematics tools;
3. use mathematics games and other mathematics-related activities to support mathematics learning;
4. develop awareness of and potential for life-long professional growth.

學生修完本科後，能夠：
1. 運用有效的資訊與傳意科技教授數學；
2. 運用教學工具設計數學教學任務；
3. 運用數學遊戲及其他數學活動輔助數學學習
4. 具備終身學習及專業成長的意識

By the end of this course, students will be able to:
1. articulate knowledge of the development of mathematical sense, algebraic thinking and geometric thinking;
2. use various problem-solving and critical-thinking techniques to set up and solve real-world applications;
3. communicate accurate mathematical terminology and notation in written and/or oral form in order to explain mathematical ideas for pedagogical purpose;
4. demonstrate understanding on the learning of mathematics from cognitive and affective aspects.

學生修完本科後，能夠:
1. 獲得關於數感，代數思維以及幾何思維發展方面的知識；
2. 運用不同解難及批判思維技巧來建立應付現實問題的方法;
3. 能有效地以書面及或口頭形式闡釋數學專門用語及符號，藉以在教學中表達數學思想；
4. 能從認知層面和情感層面增進對數學學習的理解

