By the end of this course, students will be able to:
1. know the nature of mathematics and its implications for pedagogy;
2. demonstrate the pedagogy and content knowledge in calculus and advanced mathematical thinking;
3. analyze the connections among different dimensions in school mathematics.

學生修完本科後，能夠:
1. 認識數學的本質和它在教學中的應用
2. 展示與微積分和高等數學思想相關的教學知識和學科知識;
3. 分析學校數學不同學習領域之間的關係

By the end of this course, students will be able to:
1. articulate knowledge required for teaching the concepts and procedures in the dimension of data handling;
2. devise teaching strategies to develop students’ awareness in the misuse of statistics;
3. explain the essential concepts in probability and statistics.

